HEADWORD: Water shield
<hw>Wa"ter shield`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An aquatic
American plant (<spn>Brasenia peltata</spn>) having floating oval
leaves, and the covered with a clear jelly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

